snippet.title: Official Madden 25 Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Watch the official Madden 25 release trailer now and get ready to experience a game 25 years in the making with Madden 25. Buy here: http://o.ea.com/16831 The official Madden 25 release date is August 27th on the Xbox 360 & PS3.

Music by David Dallas, entitled, "Runnin," available now at iTunes - http://smarturl.it/Runnin (courtesy of @duckdownmusic / @dawnraidmusic).
